latestIgtvVideos.title: Poochante Pyaragraph
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I was challenged by Cinemamara as a part of #PoochantePyaragraph challenge to post a video of me reading a favourite paragraph from one of  Poornachandra Tejaswi's many works. I will nominate atleast one non-reader to take up this challenge. This is to celebrate works of Tejaswi as a part of his 82nd birth anniversary . And guess what ? Best ones will be rewarded with Tejaswi merchandise by Team Cinemamara. Include the hashtags below to participate. 
#PoochantePyaragraph 
#AnnouncementSep8

I now nominate @milana.neela , @ananya.amar and @naveentejaswi to take up this challenge 😁

'Daredevil Musthafa' is coming out on the 19th of May and I'm really excited to show you guys what we've done with this! 

Pakka maja filled film coming to entertain you ♥️♥️♥️

#ddm #daredevilmusthafa #ddm_releasing_on_may19

The Poster of "Daredevil Musthafa " ♥️
This is my first feature film and it being a film from this team makes it extra special.
